metadata.name: Galaxy of my mind #1
metadata.description:
We sat in a golden plain on top of a mountain. The purple lake is in front of our eyes and we watch the scene of embracing the water and the plain.
There is a strange silence in the space.
In such a way that the sound of water kissing when hugging the plain can also be heard.
I put my head on the wings of my dragon and my body is buried in the body of the plain.
I look at the blue sky above me and the planet earth portal is visible in the distance. 
When I calm down, I close my eyes and through the portal of my mind planet immerse myself in the beauty of this endless world of imagination.
